p: The title compound was obtained in 38% yield from compound 33 followed the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.90 (s, 6H), 4.71 (s, 2H), 6.66 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.08 (d, J = 8.7 Hz, 2H), 7.20 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.43 (t, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.53 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 7.66 (d, J = 8.7 Hz, 2H), 8.01 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 8.49 (s, 1H), 9.03 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H).
